162.0, "text": " and Bailey says they took her under their wing.", "tokens": [50364, 293, 28192, 1619, 436, 1890, 720, 833, 641, 11162, 13, 50514], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.060141954781874174, "compression_ratio": 1.5747126436781609, "no_speech_prob": 0.004066492430865765}, {"id": 41, "seek": 15900, "start": 162.0, "end": 167.0, "text": " If you take somebody under your wing, you decide to protect them or guide them.", "tokens": [50514, 759, 291, 747, 2618, 833, 428, 11162, 11, 291, 4536, 281, 2371, 552, 420, 5934, 552, 13, 50764], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.060141954781874174, "compression_ratio": 1.5747126436781609, "no_speech_prob": 0.004066492430865765}, {"id": 42, "seek": 15900, "start": 167.0, "end": 170.0, "text": " Let's meet another musician, Josh.", "tokens": [50764, 961, 311, 1677, 1071, 19570, 11, 9785, 13, 50914], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.060141954781874174, "compression_ratio": 1.5747126436781609, "no_speech_prob": 0.004066492430865765}, {"id": 43, "seek": 15900, "start": 170.0, "end": 176.0, "text": " So I learnt my first proper song on guitar when I was about thirteen.", "tokens": [50914, 407, 286, 18991, 452, 700, 2296, 2153, 322, 7531, 562, 286, 390, 466, 31534, 13, 51214], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.060141954781874174, "compression_ratio": 1.5747126436781609, "no_speech_prob": 0.004066492430865765}, {"id": 44, "seek": 15900, "start": 176.0, "end": 180.0, "text": " I literally started busking the moment I could kind of do that.", "tokens": [51214, 286, 3736, 1409, 1255, 5092, 264, 1623, 286, 727, 733, 295, 360, 300, 13, 51414], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.060141954781874174, "compression_ratio": 1.5747126436781609, "no_speech_prob": 0.004066492430865765}, {"id": 45, "seek": 15900, "start": 180.0, "end": 183.0, "text": " Josh lives in London and is a busker.", "tokens": [51414, 9785, 2909, 294, 7042, 293, 307, 257, 1255, 5767, 13, 51564], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.060141954781874174, "compression_ratio": 1.5747126436781609, "no_speech_prob": 0.004066492430865765}, {"id": 46, "seek": 15900, "start": 183.0, "end": 187.0, "text": " This means that he performs on the street or in public places to earn money.", "tokens": [51564, 639, 1355, 300, 415, 26213, 322, 264, 4838, 420, 294, 1908, 3190, 281, 6012, 1460, 13, 51764], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.060141954781874174, "compression_ratio": 1.5747126436781609, "no_speech_prob": 0.004066492430865765}, {"id": 47, "seek": 18700, "start": 187.0, "end": 192.0, "text": " Busking is a common way for musicians to make money and perform to more people.", "tokens": [50364, 8006, 5092, 307, 257, 2689, 636, 337, 16916, 281, 652, 1460, 293, 2042, 281, 544, 561, 13, 50614], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08826516125653242, "compression_ratio": 1.6509803921568627, "no_speech_prob": 0.03450695052742958}, {"id": 48, "seek": 18700, "start": 192.0, "end": 196.0, "text": " And as Josh told BBC Learning English programme My Song, My Home,", "tokens": [50614, 400, 382, 9785, 1907, 22669, 15205, 3669, 14001, 1222, 11862, 11, 1222, 8719, 11, 50814], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08826516125653242, "compression_ratio": 1.6509803921568627, "no_speech_prob": 0.03450695052742958}, {"id": 49, "seek": 18700, "start": 196.0, "end": 199.0, "text": " it can help musicians to get new opportunities.", "tokens": [50814, 309, 393, 854, 16916, 281, 483, 777, 4786, 13, 50964], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08826516125653242, "compression_ratio": 1.6509803921568627, "no_speech_prob": 0.03450695052742958}, {"id": 50, "seek": 18700, "start": 199.0, "end": 205.0, "text": " It's been kind of like my main earner that's kept me going for the last ten or so years.", "tokens": [50964, 467, 311, 668, 733, 295, 411, 452, 2135, 6012, 260, 300, 311, 4305, 385, 516, 337, 264, 1036, 2064, 420, 370, 924, 13, 51264], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08826516125653242, "compression_ratio": 1.6509803921568627, "no_speech_prob": 0.03450695052742958}, {"id": 51, "seek": 18700, "start": 205.0, "end": 209.0, "text": " From that it's then got me various different opportunities.", "tokens": [51264, 3358, 300, 309, 311, 550, 658, 385, 3683, 819, 4786, 13, 51464], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08826516125653242, "compression_ratio": 1.6509803921568627, "no_speech_prob": 0.03450695052742958}, {"id": 52, "seek": 18700, "start": 209.0, "end": 214.0, "text": " It's got me all my gigs, got me all my connections, so I owe a lot to busking.", "tokens": [51464, 467, 311, 658, 385, 439, 452, 34586, 11, 658, 385, 439, 452, 9271, 11, 370, 286, 16655, 257, 688, 281, 1255, 5092, 13, 51714], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08826516125653242, "compression_ratio": 1.6509803921568627, "no_speech_prob": 0.03450695052742958}, {"id": 53, "seek": 21400, "start": 214.0, "end": 218.0, "text": " Busking is Josh's main earner. It's his main source of money.", "tokens": [50364, 8006, 5092, 307, 9785, 311, 2135, 6012, 260, 13, 467, 311, 702, 2135, 4009, 295, 1460, 13, 50564], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05522609830976607, "compression_ratio": 1.6639004149377594, "no_speech_prob": 0.023989638313651085}, {"id": 54, "seek": 21400, "start": 218.0, "end": 222.0, "text": " He says that busking has got him all his gigs and connections.", "tokens": [50564, 634, 1619, 300, 1255, 5092, 575, 658, 796, 439, 702, 34586, 293, 9271, 13, 50764], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05522609830976607, "compression_ratio": 1.6639004149377594, "no_speech_prob": 0.023989638313651085}, {"id": 55, "seek": 21400, "start": 222.0, "end": 227.0, "text": " Gigs are musical concerts and it's an informal slang word.", "tokens": [50764, 460, 17156, 366, 9165, 24924, 293, 309, 311, 364, 24342, 42517, 1349, 13, 51014], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05522609830976607, "compression_ratio": 1.6639004149377594, "no_speech_prob": 0.023989638313651085}, {"id": 56, "seek": 21400, "start": 227.0, "end": 230.0, "text": " Josh says he owes a lot to busking.", "tokens": [51014, 9785, 1619, 415, 50028, 257, 688, 281, 1255, 5092, 13, 51164], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05522609830976607, "compression_ratio": 1.6639004149377594, "no_speech_prob": 0.023989638313651085}, {"id": 57, "seek": 21400, "start": 230.0, "end": 236.0, "text": " If you owe a lot to someone or something, you have success or happiness because of that personal thing.", "tokens": [51164, 759, 291, 16655, 257, 688, 281, 1580, 420, 746, 11, 291, 362, 2245, 420, 8324, 570, 295, 300, 2973, 551, 13, 51464], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05522609830976607, "compression_ratio": 1.6639004149377594, "no_speech_prob": 0.023989638313651085}, {"id": 58, "seek": 21400, "start": 236.0, "end": 240.0, "text": " So would you like to listen to some of Josh's music, Neil?", "tokens": [51464, 407, 576, 291, 411, 281, 2140, 281, 512, 295, 9785, 311, 1318, 11, 18615, 30, 51664], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05522609830976607, "compression_ratio": 1.6639004149377594, "no_speech_prob": 0.023989638313651085}, {"id": 59, "seek": 21400, "start": 240.0, "end": 241.0, "text": " Of course I would.", "tokens": [51664, 2720, 1164, 286, 576, 13, 51714], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.05522609830976607, "compression_ratio": 1.6639004149377594, "no_speech_prob": 0.023989638313651085}, {"id": 60, "seek": 24100, "start": 241.0, "end": 244.0, "text": " Well, here's a bit of his song That Side of the Wall,", "tokens": [50364, 1042, 11, 510, 311, 257, 857, 295, 702, 2153, 663, 19026, 295, 264, 9551, 11, 50514], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1102006715886733, "compression_ratio": 1.1160714285714286, "no_speech_prob": 0.20366479456424713}, {"id": 61, "seek": 24100, "start": 244.0, "end": 248.0, "text": " which he performed for BBC Learning English programme My Song, My Home.", "tokens": [50514, 597, 415, 10332, 337, 22669, 15205, 3669, 14001, 1222, 11862, 11, 1222, 8719, 13, 50714], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1102006715886733, "compression_ratio": 1.1160714285714286, "no_speech_prob": 0.20366479456424713}, {"id": 62, "seek": 27100, "start": 271.0, "end": 274.0, "text": " Wow, Josh is pretty good, isn't he? I'd love to hear more.", "tokens": [50364, 3153, 11, 9785, 307, 1238, 665, 11, 1943, 380, 415, 30, 286, 1116, 959, 281, 1568, 544, 13, 50514], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17122307602240114, "compression_ratio": 1.448888888888889, "no_speech_prob": 0.028256606310606003}, {"id": 63, "seek": 27100, "start": 274.0, "end": 281.0, "text": " Well, you can find performances by the musicians in the series on our website, bbclanningenglish.com,", "tokens": [50514, 1042, 11, 291, 393, 915, 16087, 538, 264, 16916, 294, 264, 2638, 322, 527, 3144, 11, 272, 65, 3474, 282, 773, 1501, 1933, 13, 1112, 11, 50864], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17122307602240114, "compression_ratio": 1.448888888888889, "no_speech_prob": 0.028256606310606003}, {"id": 64, "seek": 27100, "start": 281.0, "end": 284.0, "text": " and we'll also put a link in the notes below this episode.", "tokens": [50864, 293, 321, 603, 611, 829, 257, 2113, 294, 264, 5570, 2507, 341, 3500, 13, 51014], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17122307602240114, "compression_ratio": 1.448888888888889, "no_speech_prob": 0.028256606310606003}, {"id": 65, "seek": 27100, "start": 284.0, "end": 287.0, "text": " OK, so what about your question, Pippa?", "tokens": [51014, 2264, 11, 370, 437, 466, 428, 1168, 11, 430, 2488, 64, 30, 51164], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17122307602240114, "compression_ratio": 1.448888888888889, "no_speech_prob": 0.028256606310606003}, {"id": 66, "seek": 27100, "start": 287.0, "end": 292.0, "text": " Yes, I asked which artist had the most number one songs in the UK,", "tokens": [51164, 1079, 11, 286, 2351, 597, 5748, 632, 264, 881, 1230, 472, 5781, 294, 264, 7051, 11, 51414], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.17122307602240114, "compression_ratio": 1.448888888888889, "no_speech_prob": 0.028256606310606003}, {"id": 67, "seek": 29200, "start": 293.0, "end": 296.0, "text": " OK, so what about your question, Pippa?", "tokens": [50414, 2264, 11, 370, 437, 466, 428, 1168, 11, 430, 2488, 64, 30, 50564], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10843981726694915, "compression_ratio": 1.5775193798449612, "no_speech_prob": 0.34102529287338257}, {"id": 68, "seek": 29200, "start": 296.0, "end": 301.0, "text": " Yes, I asked which artist had the most number one songs in the UK charts,", "tokens": [50564, 1079, 11, 286, 2351, 597, 5748, 632, 264, 881, 1230, 472, 5781, 294, 264, 7051, 17767, 11, 50814], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10843981726694915, "compression_ratio": 1.5775193798449612, "no_speech_prob": 0.34102529287338257}, {"id": 69, "seek": 29200, "start": 301.0, "end": 306.0, "text": " The Beatles, Ed Sheeran or Elvis Presley, and you said The Beatles, Neil.", "tokens": [50814, 440, 38376, 11, 3977, 1240, 260, 282, 420, 39944, 2718, 3420, 11, 293, 291, 848, 440, 38376, 11, 18615, 13, 51064], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10843981726694915, "compression_ratio": 1.5775193798449612, "no_speech_prob": 0.34102529287338257}, {"id": 70, "seek": 29200, "start": 306.0, "end": 309.0, "text": " But the answer is actually Elvis Presley.", "tokens": [51064, 583, 264, 1867, 307, 767, 39944, 2718, 3420, 13, 51214], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10843981726694915, "compression_ratio": 1.5775193798449612, "no_speech_prob": 0.34102529287338257}, {"id": 71, "seek": 29200, "start": 309.0, "end": 314.0, "text": " He's had 21 number one songs and The Beatles have had 18.", "tokens": [51214, 634, 311, 632, 5080, 1230, 472, 5781, 293, 440, 38376, 362, 632, 2443, 13, 51464], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10843981726694915, "compression_ratio": 1.5775193798449612, "no_speech_prob": 0.34102529287338257}, {"id": 72, "seek": 29200, "start": 314.0, "end": 317.0, "text": " Really? Well, that's OK. I love The King as well.", "tokens": [51464, 4083, 30, 1042, 11, 300, 311, 2264, 13, 286, 959, 440, 3819, 382, 731, 13, 51614], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10843981726694915, "compression_ratio": 1.5775193798449612, "no_speech_prob": 0.34102529287338257}, {"id": 73, "seek": 29200, "start": 317.0, "end": 321.0, "text": " OK, let's recap the vocabulary we've learned in this musical episode.", "tokens": [51614, 2264, 11, 718, 311, 20928, 264, 19864, 321, 600, 3264, 294, 341, 9165, 3500, 13, 51814], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.10843981726694915, "compression_ratio": 1.5775193798449612, "no_speech_prob": 0.34102529287338257}, {"id": 74, "seek": 32100, "start": 321.0, "end": 327.0, "text": " Starting with open mic nights, events where anyone can sing or play music.", "tokens": [50364, 16217, 365, 1269, 3123, 13249, 11, 3931, 689, 2878, 393, 1522, 420, 862, 1318, 13, 50664], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06598280497959681, "compression_ratio": 1.7098039215686274, "no_speech_prob": 0.16826866567134857}, {"id": 75, "seek": 32100, "start": 327.0, "end": 332.0, "text": " Songwriter circles are meetings for people interested in writing their own music.", "tokens": [50664, 11862, 23681, 13040, 366, 8410, 337, 561, 3102, 294, 3579, 641, 1065, 1318, 13, 50914], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06598280497959681, "compression_ratio": 1.7098039215686274, "no_speech_prob": 0.16826866567134857}, {"id": 76, "seek": 32100, "start": 332.0, "end": 334.0, "text": " A bunch of people is a group of people.", "tokens": [50914, 316, 3840, 295, 561, 307, 257, 1594, 295, 561, 13, 51014], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06598280497959681, "compression_ratio": 1.7098039215686274, "no_speech_prob": 0.16826866567134857}, {"id": 77, "seek": 32100, "start": 334.0, "end": 339.0, "text": " The expression take someone under your wing means to protect or guide someone.", "tokens": [51014, 440, 6114, 747, 1580, 833, 428, 11162, 1355, 281, 2371, 420, 5934, 1580, 13, 51264], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06598280497959681, "compression_ratio": 1.7098039215686274, "no_speech_prob": 0.16826866567134857}, {"id": 78, "seek": 32100, "start": 339.0, "end": 342.0, "text": " Busking is performing in a public place for money,", "tokens": [51264, 8006, 5092, 307, 10205, 294, 257, 1908, 1081, 337, 1460, 11, 51414], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06598280497959681, "compression_ratio": 1.7098039215686274, "no_speech_prob": 0.16826866567134857}, {"id": 79, "seek": 32100, "start": 342.0, "end": 346.0, "text": " and a busker is someone who performs on the street for money.", "tokens": [51414, 293, 257, 1255, 5767, 307, 1580, 567, 26213, 322, 264, 4838, 337, 1460, 13, 51614], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06598280497959681, "compression_ratio": 1.7098039215686274, "no_speech_prob": 0.16826866567134857}, {"id": 80, "seek": 32100, "start": 346.0, "end": 349.0, "text": " Your main earner is your main source of income.", "tokens": [51614, 2260, 2135, 6012, 260, 307, 428, 2135, 4009, 295, 5742, 13, 51764], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.06598280497959681, "compression_ratio": 1.7098039215686274, "no_speech_prob": 0.16826866567134857}, {"id": 81, "seek": 34900, "start": 350.0, "end": 352.0, "text": " Gigs are musical concerts.", "tokens": [50414, 460, 17156, 366, 9165, 24924, 13, 50514], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08457469118052516, "compression_ratio": 1.5978260869565217, "no_speech_prob": 0.0563075877726078}, {"id": 82, "seek": 34900, "start": 352.0, "end": 355.0, "text": " And the expression to owe a lot to someone or something", "tokens": [50514, 400, 264, 6114, 281, 16655, 257, 688, 281, 1580, 420, 746, 50664], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08457469118052516, "compression_ratio": 1.5978260869565217, "no_speech_prob": 0.0563075877726078}, {"id": 83, "seek": 34900, "start": 355.0, "end": 359.0, "text": " means to have success or happiness because of that personal thing.", "tokens": [50664, 1355, 281, 362, 2245, 420, 8324, 570, 295, 300, 2973, 551, 13, 50864], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08457469118052516, "compression_ratio": 1.5978260869565217, "no_speech_prob": 0.0563075877726078}, {"id": 84, "seek": 34900, "start": 359.0, "end": 361.0, "text": " Once again, our six minutes are up,", "tokens": [50864, 3443, 797, 11, 527, 2309, 2077, 366, 493, 11, 50964], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08457469118052516, "compression_ratio": 1.5978260869565217, "no_speech_prob": 0.0563075877726078}, {"id": 85, "seek": 34900, "start": 361.0, "end": 367.0, "text": " but you can find My Song, My Home on our website, bbclearningenglish.com.", "tokens": [50964, 457, 291, 393, 915, 1222, 11862, 11, 1222, 8719, 322, 527, 3144, 11, 272, 65, 2160, 2341, 1501, 1933, 13, 1112, 13, 51264], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08457469118052516, "compression_ratio": 1.5978260869565217, "no_speech_prob": 0.0563075877726078}, {"id": 86, "seek": 34900, "start": 367.0, "end": 371.0, "text": " Watch the songs and sing along and learn more about the vocabulary in the lyrics.", "tokens": [51264, 7277, 264, 5781, 293, 1522, 2051, 293, 1466, 544, 466, 264, 19864, 294, 264, 12189, 13, 51464], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08457469118052516, "compression_ratio": 1.5978260869565217, "no_speech_prob": 0.0563075877726078}, {"id": 87, "seek": 34900, "start": 371.0, "end": 376.0, "text": " We'll see you again soon for some more trending topics and useful vocabulary.", "tokens": [51464, 492, 603, 536, 291, 797, 2321, 337, 512, 544, 28692, 8378, 293, 4420, 19864, 13, 51714], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08457469118052516, "compression_ratio": 1.5978260869565217, "no_speech_prob": 0.0563075877726078}, {"id": 88, "seek": 34900, "start": 376.0, "end": 377.0, "text": " Bye for now.", "tokens": [51714, 4621, 337, 586, 13, 51764], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08457469118052516, "compression_ratio": 1.5978260869565217, "no_speech_prob": 0.0563075877726078}, {"id": 89, "seek": 34900, "start": 377.0, "end": 378.0, "text": " Goodbye.", "tokens": [51764, 15528, 13, 51814], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.08457469118052516, "compression_ratio": 1.5978260869565217, "no_speech_prob": 0.0563075877726078}, {"id": 90, "seek": 37900, "start": 379.0, "end": 384.0, "text": " Six Minute English from bbclearningenglish.com", "tokens": [50364, 11678, 33509, 3669, 490, 272, 65, 2160, 2341, 1501, 1933, 13, 1112, 50614], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.2725429852803548, "compression_ratio": 0.92, "no_speech_prob": 0.9306111335754395}], "language": "en"}